  "detailed_description": "<h1>PLAY PROLOGUE NOW!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1772525515\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Ruiga Pirates is a survivors-like game. Hellish seas, pirates everywhere and you can't escape sea creatures. All you can do is fight to the death and take what you can and leave nothing behind. Collect gold on every run to buy upgrades, new ships and find skilled captains. Get ready for seven seas challenges!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/b7d213b0dd7159b316835facf92266e4.avif?t=1772525515\" width=614 height=96 /></span><br><br>Choose your ship and captain. Customize your enhancements. Your choices will make you live more and make you shoot more. Prevent enemy ships from approaching you. Avoid fires and watch out for traps. Complete challenges and explore hidden treasures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/7bc4cce85d93db82f08973e0d3565b04.poster.avif?t=1772525515\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/7bc4cce85d93db82f08973e0d3565b04.webm?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/7bc4cce85d93db82f08973e0d3565b04.mp4?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With the missions you will take, you will sometimes bomb an island and sometimes go after the most wanted pirates. Get ready for legends of krakens, mermaids and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/b3457ed495459a10aa16b74065166d50.avif?t=1772525515\" width=614 height=96 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/323746320accab037a421dbe3a7787f1.avif?t=1772525515\" width=614 height=330 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/3e38651baea748d78be033870ca49516.poster.avif?t=1772525515\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/3e38651baea748d78be033870ca49516.webm?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/3e38651baea748d78be033870ca49516.mp4?t=1772525515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461580/extras/3db159155efe676924396fcba97c5f0d.avif?t=1772525515\" width=614 height=96 /></span>",
